The paper discusses a method for exact structure learning of Bayesian networks, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). The problem of Bayesian network structure learning is also related to data mining (cs.DM) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper proposes a new approach that improves the runtime and memory consumption of existing algorithms, which is a topic related to systems and control (cs.SI).
